# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented here.

---

## [1.0.0] - 2026-03-30

### Added
- Initial release of AppPermissionsReport.ps1
- Exports Delegated and Application permissions for all App Registrations
- Hashtable-based SP lookup for improved performance
- Null-safe permission value handling (returns "UNKNOWN" if not found)
- Auto-creates output folder if it does not exist
